<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #f4f7f5; margin: 0; padding: 0; color: #333; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 580px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1rem; }
    .card { background: white; border-radius: 16px; padding: 2.5rem 2rem; box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.07); }
    .wordmark { font-family: Georgia, serif; font-style: italic; font-size: 26px; font-weight: bold; color: #013f3a; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; display: block; }
    .wordmark span { color: #FBB718; }
    p { font-size: 0.97rem; line-height: 1.75; color: #444; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
    .links { margin: 1.75rem 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }
    .link-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; background: #f4f7f5; border-radius: 12px; padding: 0.9rem 1.1rem; text-decoration: none; color: #013f3a; }
    .link-row__icon { font-size: 1.4rem; line-height: 1; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .link-row__label { font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; color: #888; display: block; }
    .link-row__text { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; color: #013f3a; display: block; }
    .survey-note { background: rgba(251,183,24,0.10); border-left: 3px solid #FBB718; border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0; padding: 0.9rem 1.1rem; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
    .survey-note p { margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #555; }
    .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.75rem; color: #aaa; }
    .footer a { color: #6aaa8a; text-decoration: none; }
    a { color: #013f3a; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="card">
      <span class="wordmark">gooi<span>*</span></span>

      <p>Good day <%= @recipient_name %></p>

      <p>
        We are thrilled to hear that <%= @block.name %> is considering an organic waste service for its
        residents. What a wonderful step forward in sustainability.
      </p>

      <p>
        We have quite a bit of experience in setting these systems up and would love to work with you
        to make it a reality.
      </p>

      <p>
        I have put together a short presentation you can share with your group of trustees, as well as a
        quotation that covers the organic waste of the entire estate — including weekly collection and
        processing, bins that would live in your refuse area, and countertop buckets for each unit.
      </p>

      <div class="links">
        <%= link_to @deck_url, class: "link-row" do %>
          <span class="link-row__icon">📋</span>
          <span>
            <span class="link-row__label">Presentation</span>
            <span class="link-row__text">View the estate deck →</span>
          </span>
        <% end %>

        <%= link_to @quotation_url, class: "link-row" do %>
          <span class="link-row__icon">📄</span>
          <span>
            <span class="link-row__label">Quotation #<%= @quotation.number %></span>
            <span class="link-row__text">View the full quote →</span>
          </span>
        <% end %>

        <%= link_to @survey_url, class: "link-row" do %>
          <span class="link-row__icon">📝</span>
          <span>
            <span class="link-row__label">Resident survey</span>
            <span class="link-row__text">Share with residents →</span>
          </span>
        <% end %>
      </div>

      <div class="survey-note">
        <p>
          <strong>A note on the phased approach:</strong> In our experience it is unlikely that all
          residents adopt the practice immediately. We can run the rollout in phases so you are not paying
          for processing volume that isn't being used. The resident survey above helps us understand who is
          ready to start immediately and whether they need a countertop bucket. Based on the results we may
          find half the estate is ready to go, with the rest joining after the initial 6 month subscription.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p>
        If you have any questions or would like to have a call to discuss, please feel free to let me know.
      </p>

      <p>Looking forward to hearing from you.</p>

      <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem; color: #888; font-size: 0.85rem;">
        Kristen<br>
        <a href="mailto:howzit@gooi.me">howzit@gooi.me</a> · 083 635 3126
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        Gooi · Cape Town's kitchen scrap collection ·
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/gooi_capetown/">@gooi_capetown</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
